# ── GA4 Analytics ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# REQUIRED: Replace G-XXXXXXXXXX with your real GA4 Measurement ID.
#
# HOW TO SET UP:
#   1. Go to analytics.google.com
#   2. Admin → Create Property → Web stream
#   3. Copy the Measurement ID (format: G-XXXXXXXXXX)
#   4. Add it as a GitHub Actions secret:
#      Repository → Settings → Secrets and variables → Actions → New secret
#      Name: GA_MEASUREMENT_ID  |  Value: G-XXXXXXXXXX
#
# For local dev: copy this file to .env and fill in your real ID.
# The build script (npm run ga:inject) will update all HTML files automatically.
GA_MEASUREMENT_ID=G-XXXXXXXXXX

# ── Volunteer Signup Endpoint ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Optional: Set this to your email capture API endpoint.
# Supported: EmailOctopus, Mailchimp, ActBlue Accounts, custom API, Google Forms webhook.
# If left as placeholder, forms fall back to mailto: (opens email client).
# Add as GitHub Actions secret named SIGNUP_ENDPOINT if using a real API.
# SIGNUP_ENDPOINT=https://emailoctopus.com/api/1.6/lists/YOUR_LIST_ID/contacts
